    "16375796157ce93592": {
      "type": "text-with-image",
      "settings": {
        "subheading": "Our presentation box",
        "title": "Gifting",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/D813755_copy.png",
        "image_position": "left",
        "content": "<p>All our gloves come with a storage bag for safe keeping. All orders are delivered in our presentation box which is, like our gloves, built to last. For us, it's about the product, not the packaging, but when we designed our box we made sure it was beautiful and we chose the colour, '<a href=\"https:\/\/www.corneliajames.com\/blogs\/information\/our-promise\">light cockpit green<\/a>' to symbolise a style that endures. If the gloves are a gift for somebody special, we'll be happy to include a handwritten note - just let us know in the order notes section during checkout.<\/p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": ""
      }
    },
    "16375865754b194dbb": {
      "type": "text-with-image",
      "settings": {
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "Sizing Your gloves",
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Group_6_1_1024x1024_f3275d48-e913-4472-986d-f326f6de2128.png",
        "image_position": "right",
        "content": "<p>All our gloves are made with a glove size from 6 to 8½, and for our longer gloves we include an arm fit to ensure the correct sizing<\/p><p><em><strong>To ascertain your glove size: <\/strong><\/em><br\/>Pass a tape measure around the widest part of your hand - usually over your knuckles, excluding the thumb. The result, in inches, is your glove size - e.g. if your hand measures 7 inches, you are a glove size 7. If you are between two sizes, round down to the lower of the two.<\/p><p><em><strong>Buying gloves for someone?<br\/><\/strong><\/em>Of course, there are times when you might not know the glove size, perhaps if you are buying our gloves as a gift. In that case, we would recommend a size 7, because this is the average size, and is likely to fit most people. Of course, if your glove doesn't fit perfectly, we are more than happy to exchange it - just <a href=\"https:\/\/www.corneliajames.com\/pages\/contact\" title=\"Contact Us\">contact us<\/a>, and we will do our best to help. Special size requirements are always available on request.<\/p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": ""
      }
    }
